https://www.sfml-dev.org/tutorials/2.6/

required packages for sfml

    freetype
    x11
    xrandr
    udev
    opengl
    flac
    ogg
    vorbis
    vorbisenc
    vorbisfile
    openal
    pthread

/usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/cmake/SFML
there in file SFMLConfig.cmake is all required information for SFML as part of cmake project

find_package
https://cmake.org/cmake/help/latest/guide/using-dependencies/index.html#guide:Using%20Dependencies%20Guide

